Creates a slackware package from the mounted Guest additions installer
using slacktrack.

To use this 'slackbuild' do the following:

- Copy these files onto a VirtualBox VM running Slackware
- Choose the VB menu option "Install Guest Additions CD Image"
- mount /dev/dvd /mnt/cdrom
- cp /mnt/cdrom/VBoxLinuxAdditions.run .
- execute ./virtualbox-addons.SlackBuild
- Your package will appear in /tmp.

